    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1935-12-04T16:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1935-12-04T16:00:00-05:00" n="424"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d424">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">701.9111/458: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hornibrook</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-12-04T16:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 4, 1935—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>33. Your 42, December 3, 5 p.m. In reply to the <hi rend="italic">note
                        verbale</hi> under reference you may state that the information desired by
                    the Iranian Government in this matter should properly be sought through its
                    representative in Washington who is in a position to furnish his Government with
                    full details of the incident and of the action thus far taken by this Government
                    as well as the steps which may subsequently be taken by the Maryland
                    authorities.</p>
                <p>The Department will in due course furnish you with complete information on this
                    subject but considers that for the present at least the matter should be handled
                    with the Iranian Government solely through its representative here.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
